description:
* More bonus levels coming soon! *

A unique puzzler that is sure to bend your brain and capture your heart!

Quell has been critically-acclaimed for its 70-plus levels of ingenious gameplay, gorgeous art style, and custom-written soundtrack (by renowned composer Steven Cravis). 

"We certainly recommend it to puzzle fans" - www.SlideToPlay.com 

"Unique 'mature' style, solid puzzle gameplay, perfectly judged learning curve" - www.Gamezebo.com. 

Try Quell today, and fall in love with this enchanting experience...
